---
title: Ginger & Coconut Chicken Curry with Garlic Rice & Crispy Shallots
description: Thai cuisine is genius about using aromatics to add flavour. Here, we’ve doubled up on superstar ingredients, with fragrant garlic in the rice so it smells and tastes like a tropical holiday, plus an addition of makrut lime leaves in the curry for a delicious touch of citrus.

*Unfortunately, this week's broccolini was in short supply, so we've replaced it with broccoli. Don't worry, the recipe will be just as delicious!*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/ginger-coconut-chicken-curry-40c0fef3.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipecards/card/ginger-coconut-chicken-curry-5fd6d9ef1363ed37736f2bcf-aef46595.pdf
